<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Congratulations — {{company}}</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #334155;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 32px 30px 28px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      }
      .header p {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 32px 30px;
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background: #f0fdf4;
        border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box .label {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #64748b;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .highlight-box .value {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #166534;
      }
      .info-grid {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .info-card {
        flex: 1;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
      }
      .info-card .label {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #64748b;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .info-card .value {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e293b;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #3b82f6;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h2>🎉 Congratulations!</h2>
        <p>{{company}} — Offer Letter</p>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>
          We are thrilled to inform you that you have been
          <strong>officially accepted</strong>
          for the following position:
        </p>

        <div class='highlight-box'>
          <div class='label'>Position</div>
          <div class='value'>{{position}}</div>
        </div>

        <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin: 20px 0;">
          <tr>
            <td width="48%" style="background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px;">
              <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px;">Start Date</div>
              <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b;">{{startDate}}</div>
            </td>
            <td width="4%"></td>
            <td width="48%" style="background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px;">
              <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px;">Department</div>
              <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b;">{{department}}</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <p>
          Your skills and experience truly stood out during the recruitment process,
          and we are confident you will be a valuable addition to our team.
        </p>

        <hr class='divider' />

        <p style='font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;'>
          Our HR team will contact you shortly with further onboarding details.
          If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reply to this email.
        </p>

        <p>
          We look forward to working with you!
        </p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          <strong>{{company}} HR Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        © 2026 {{company}}. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>